org.apache.drill.metastore.expressions

Interface FilterExpression.Visitor<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type into which FilterExpression will be transformed
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FilterExpressionVisitor
    Enclosing interface:
    FilterExpression

    public static interface FilterExpression.Visitor<T>
    Transforms FilterExpression implementations into suitable for Metastore implementation representation. Is handy when needed to traverse through complex filter expressions.
